{{primary sources|date=July 2017}} The '''National Chicken Council''' ('''NCC''') is a non-profit trade association based in Washington, D.C. that represents the interests of the [[United States]] [[chicken]] industry to the [[United States Congress]] and United States federal agencies.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/national-chicken-council-comment-on-consumer-reports-article-chicken-is-safe-78129522.html |title=National Chicken Council Comment on Consumer Reports Article: 'Chicken Is Safe' |access-date=2011-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111110181445/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/national-chicken-council-comment-on-consumer-reports-article-chicken-is-safe-78129522.html |archive-date=2011-11-10 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref>
The members of the NCC include chicken producers and processors, poultry distributors, and industry firms. Chicken producers and processors in the NCC account for approximately 95 percent of the chickens produced in the United States.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eatchicken.com/about-us.aspx|title=About the National Chicken Council, EatChicken.com|website=www.eatchicken.com|access-date=2011-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111010082218/http://www.eatchicken.com/about-us.aspx|archive-date=2011-10-10|dead-url=yes|df=}}</ref> Issues important to the council include [[biosecurity]] in the poultry industry and [[avian influenza]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eatchicken.com/index.aspx|title=Chicken Recipes and Nutrition Information, Eat Chicken|website=www.eatchicken.com|access-date=2011-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111010075317/http://www.eatchicken.com/index.aspx|archive-date=2011-10-10|dead-url=yes|df=}}</ref> The council sponsors EatChicken.com, a website providing chicken recipes, cooking tips, [[food safety]] information and [[propaganda]]. In October 2011, Lampkin Butts, president and CEO of [[Sanderson Farms]], was named the Chairman of the National Chicken Council. He will serve for one year.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldpoultry.net/news/people-butts-to-lead-national-chicken-council-9496.html|title=People: Butts to lead National Chicken Council |publisher=National Chicken Council}}</ref>
